subject: Baseball (College)
College World Series
lead_paragraph: Brandon Waddell limited Vanderbilt (50-21) to five hits in his first nine-inning complete game, and the Cavaliers (53-15) evened the College World Series finals with a 7-2 victory in Omaha.
